title: Nasa discovers the TRAPPIST-1 Star with 7 Earth-size planets in its orbit, in pictures
text:
Previous slide Next slide 1 of 15 View All Skip Ad 
Nasa have released this artist's concept of TRAPPIST-1, an ultra-cool dwarf star, and the seven Earth-size planets orbiting it. 
TRAPPIST-1e, f and g dwell in the so-called habitable zone, or Goldilocks zone (shown here in green) where astronomers have calculated that temperatures are just right for liquid water to pool on the surface of an Earth-like world. NASA / PA
